REQUIREMENTS
============
Python >= 2.5 and PyGTK with GTK >= 2.12.


INSTALLATION
============
This are instructions for unix-likes:

> python setup.py install --prefix=/usr/local

You can change the prefix as you like.
If everything went OK you can start the program by typing

> crosswordpuzzle.py


RUNNING WITHOUT INSTALLATION
============================
You can also simply unpack the file, enter the cwp directory and type

> python crosswordpuzzle.py

This might even work on Windows. Dunno.


